                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi> 
                     <hi rend="italic">of a Common Assault.</hi>
                  </rs>—</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18500916-1610-punishment-46" type="punishmentDescription">
