               </p>
               <p>(There were two other indictments for <rs id="t18500916-1610-offence-2" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18500916-1610-offence-2" type="offenceCategory" value="breakingPeace"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18500916-1610-offence-2" type="offenceSubcategory" value="assault"></interp>assaulting Clark</rs> and <rs id="t18500916-1610-offence-3" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18500916-1610-offence-3" type="offenceCategory" value="breakingPeace"></interp>
